{"tid":2513293,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"\"極多圖\"尖沙咀不忘老細威脅前員工,員工爆料","createTime":"2021-05-02T11:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T11:51:44.000Z","uid":337199,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a6b15d94cbf17969916bf64e3fea9756bcff4c72","tid":2513293,"uid":337199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:39:02.000Z","msg":"我就係個前員工 事源係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQcrZe2fEX4cy2T1GFXXXY3bSh18WWhP72V7TD534jf4o?filename=J3X9WFX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ3X9WFX.jpg&h=65504ef7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXL5Ruo5HScZ3hV4iZWXEArgAJCnF7qXWDU5eTQuzfWgM?filename=7VqvF7M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7VqvF7M.jpg&h=f0deeaeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所以我就去咗勞工處到落案僱主拖欠薪金<br />\n向積金局追討返佢無交嘅強積金(佢有好多個月無供)<br />\n<span class=\"red\">結果佢就話要用我啲個人資料黎威脅我</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmdqhq5MRzsvXZnVcE3buQ87Ust9sXD3bWRY7msddmGCBE?filename=kytxaW1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkytxaW1.jpg&h=a9e66f5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\">佢不仁 我不義</span> <br />\n<strong>一</strong>,用大陸豬肉呃人係泰國豬肉<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmd9hL2HttpW5ozCtutzXi42ew4H1vGka1sZv845Yn7QMC?filename=o92mNGa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo92mNGa.jpg&h=4a88e29c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmV7gqseUDPtu4jHYRwk42k8GK2JMZ6qWTriUosjUA9Djd?filename=M8TQF1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM8TQF1a.jpg&h=ce656df4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSVupduNN6pj7Zr1Xq5V3KM5mAC2feNgqhUpa6YjMM9yt?filename=q7zPWzw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq7zPWzw.jpg&h=76c7f5de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>二</strong>,<span class=\"red\">極多老鼠(大量老鼠圖慎點) </span> <br />\n由上年5月份開始就有老鼠嘅出現<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNbcPs6bXnyCZM2wvmJ3ZEpCaaWRgPBSQ4XRNtyGbL6Rm?filename=p4aPcKH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp4aPcKH.jpg&h=2f378696&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXtyRYy7nNpwra1TaTUTrXYgvmNpMRtsm7Ui6SKLi7gNw?filename=bZb3hbm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbZb3hbm.jpg&h=8572294d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTo4uv5PyCrjV8vR3jrPtdZg4AbBBwtLqj8xymtVVn13Y?filename=MNqfSKH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMNqfSKH.jpg&h=17844640&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQRZXVeAVVpdrH99z7S8WUSiegn9fdT7eEqvTXCfcBxzq?filename=y5H6eX1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy5H6eX1.jpg&h=4a429909&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTD9ZCPTVspt1LAMfZXehcis6WvkrmiKaWWby4UBDQ6Dm?filename=5QhNJRm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5QhNJRm.jpg&h=9a651319&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdnEGJbdazrPMvd58L9UeBQtrhp166Q519PYMqFwUtWzT?filename=5TDpL4G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5TDpL4G.jpg&h=aabca09e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmU1EdBfKD7dgCVw1osAZ4HMtRRaNcGvv3ahZBPdCgkrNJ?filename=9Gwe8h1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Gwe8h1.jpg&h=3469784d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaW3SGEEGCLC7W5hdTLAnNpfpMcTx95Po7PXqyYAwAxpX?filename=XJVGOh2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXJVGOh2.jpg&h=a5e94eef&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYaYKeN4v3VZ25Cvm1gp9kPWm1HSmnWFCx2runW5ViQm7?filename=1dOhmC2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1dOhmC2.jpg&h=01231a2c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZGGpaNdSd51btRUqjPbuKxYRqUr5gzu6mwraENGZ9ihp?filename=6S3dEpG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6S3dEpG.jpg&h=9a3825ee&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdDPCqZJPMsREdhbFmBTKUeJ6XnCrixdwGu3vrmPHdsJF?filename=i2qzoRm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi2qzoRm.jpg&h=84d4d85e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSsuocJrUg5Quu4ZSyQGkgBqcFbeusdTKwfjjAztgwngs?filename=GpLGOh1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGpLGOh1.jpg&h=c0494f02&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmaw8e2HUkXVntcpnCMY7K3hXDqLWuuXmykLa6FQd8LVje?filename=a2ugCbk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa2ugCbk.jpg&h=6cd65ed0&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRrbtZrx9ebumjVqCgNTxZhF1FeojkAKTXLT8sw9UibpG?filename=V2H9Xbm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV2H9Xbm.jpg&h=1ba202f4&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZ2HSF5h7JUcrzCKwAg5GWLAQtXTfZ8gPihvyMA6jmRCU?filename=c3u4L4G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3u4L4G.jpg&h=efe8ecb5&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSmWFmMxASbLE5Uh8oMWrapfM2UrPSCE7wKA4QK19t8E5?filename=9iLvGC1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9iLvGC1.jpg&h=28b8cda3&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUSYFSqdaeq2xGFAF7QFk87Epi3EYJnUvb8k2i3eCGe79?filename=2cHeoRm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2cHeoRm.jpg&h=8c75fa42&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呢個兜我當時係擲咗,但後尾我聽同事講,店長攞返起黎用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(個兜平時會攞黎撈餃子餡/食材)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTFoHzeBxnvNtxT9AAarht4yhGA9MjoGKfDSiEjeRuq2z?filename=9KJ9cW9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9KJ9cW9.jpg&h=3568d0b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUDj6xMXm4tMqW8AQmH89e4tMKzY9zT2UQ6jk85LiwcnQ?filename=y3EDQKF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy3EDQKF.jpg&h=80866877&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<strong>三</strong>,<span class=\"red\">老鼠屎</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYCaG868HcqnWtEHsxAzPfkvRc5oMJeV7yiFwCwF6ECz8?filename=oR16Zw8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoR16Zw8.jpg&h=c5ae065c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVvfq1qQNJpHJSZ29xE9sGnX2b1TXGs9FrZ3VcXMUNzgp?filename=AieXmLt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAieXmLt.jpg&h=4647b529&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXQSHgK8KaEyBqNAfjkaMxSwdATiNLMopxNFjVVrESGbt?filename=0oUsJYO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0oUsJYO.jpg&h=b32756ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQumx1tZtpjGDNbvdE8Cjh7oq9b2kqbmhxYmkmsdbd1pw?filename=tPmCmLt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtPmCmLt.jpg&h=62054d46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdQEAS1BsHq9iEDDbNXg7KXdHV8qe5RoP5XNhgESWnBHa?filename=SjcFjw8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSjcFjw8.jpg&h=5f66f9df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQpYehzRLYcLVRsqseSy9YLHi2igYJ7nNQnkSXQy9pw1j?filename=axMSaDO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaxMSaDO.jpg&h=a6ed9551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmX893mQotmFZRrqkEofZQbRmsn2DFYyFGUqac452PiEmD?filename=gOx9XiO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgOx9XiO.jpg&h=fd8c763e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbfGGD1GJQ6mveYi8kXTQTbwZxvSsxpi2RsUhcHKuUorA?filename=TcQfSR8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTcQfSR8.jpg&h=9f3010a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmP5WyJypwL43a9jm4ECWYFa9RToHM3SXuJSuYHGHLzRfb?filename=qcNNJYO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqcNNJYO.jpg&h=6b5fb679&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNPKEVMdCwkpvuqsrPfC4nQ99LsyzDC7NitapHQMd5Qmv?filename=bwhFjw8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbwhFjw8.jpg&h=eb063eb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeJzN5DQE99zSbfgbLJVwHU3iBpz4Ky8aWCKcNgksSp26?filename=5zdhmSf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5zdhmSf.jpg&h=4261ffe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmegANvYkXFf6MGY1K4rnQgWVbZcFtJmnuj1FBN6VM1TUb?filename=jMVjAcf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjMVjAcf.jpg&h=92da592c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一直有向老細反映老鼠問題,但佢一直都係得過且過就算,完全無認真正視過問題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPQ9A1fmsFq4cBcSkDGrWrikte5ZRRiHwC8E9KqEoeXE6?filename=wRb6ZrO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwRb6ZrO.jpg&h=37a2713c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n直到有一次朝早有兩枱客人食緊野嘅時候,有隻老鼠彈咗出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嚇到個客彈起身,即刻比錢走人<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWY5ST82EgTZq8wbKKN91asAtaRftqQsPNKdLopED1xkW?filename=goZo1GD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgoZo1GD.jpg&h=10580516&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呢件事之後我同同事上網搵咗滅鼠公司,情況先開始有改善<br />\n<span class=\"red\">以上所有老鼠圖,全部都有send過比老細睇</span><br />\n <br />\n<strong>四</strong>,另外相信近一兩個月有黎過堂食嘅朋友都會聞到一陣陣嘅臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,因為雪櫃由後巷搬咗出黎,而個雪櫃係唔凍嘅,所以放係雪櫃入面嘅肉類會出血水變壞,之後發出惡臭味,<br />\n但會繼續用,比啲客食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,包括你哋飲緊佢講所謂嘅無味精雞湯(其實係會落大量雞粉)嘅湯骨同雞,<br />\n腸粉用嘅肥牛<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmefdEgo3ZC9wFGsic3BBFMACy3kp8mUi9qHwiX6Nu9K3g?filename=6kMuXqW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6kMuXqW.jpg&h=dcd17d7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTULP2KMuC7CoPjdqg3nLzLQ4qBS1TUYBcogXCSFUcjBg?filename=HJkcaLV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHJkcaLV.jpg&h=a5b0f7b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTuizg4WJY5p8sUaAyS44WTQiCSsMdj1G9jnia75DpZyJ?filename=sFOX6jf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsFOX6jf.jpg&h=e47628a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWviCcp2urHDj6kSVKerjMmATVrdBFznnNx1CRBaLreDT?filename=7TuMfc6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7TuMfc6.jpg&h=091636eb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有基本上舖頭7成嘅野都係淘寶/大陸野<br />\n包括生餃嘅12格,18格環保盒,辣椒醬玻璃樽,雪櫃,鐵兜,豬肉丸,牛肉丸,等等都係<br />\n<br />\n最後佢講過當佢哋只係一間不是藍的食店,用意係咩,大家自己諗<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmc7MQopn8LXSPdC841G7cxSytwCuxhDwUSdqy7AM6hpzC?filename=V8nFjL1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV8nFjL1.jpg&h=9f975142&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">以上句句屬實,唔通我離職後,追討返屬於我嘅野,就要受你嘅威脅?<br />\n我絕不妥協</span>"},{"pid":"c3da3408073bff08e8f27eaef826a3b85e27c863","tid":2513293,"uid":337199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:39:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7417cafaaa0aadd2cb251344a3263dfc93745972","tid":2513293,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:43:14.000Z","msg":"廸廸尼樂園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d6070f47742c5de014d38df74a077f7e566c42","tid":2513293,"uid":24523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:43:50.000Z","msg":"唔知咩事<br />\n但係照推咗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a8daf56b43b3c546e357ad28e03849dd1bcdfb2","tid":2513293,"uid":231957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:43:50.000Z","msg":"老鼠 咁既環境 汁左佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e7064d8574b8e8ba0f8173a32348000966c2f6","tid":2513293,"uid":98671,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:44:05.000Z","msg":"好撚長 睇得出你好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫你推比其他巴打睇"},{"pid":"ea1f4045c7d52de446a1cb8125fe3c25d8f94e1b","tid":2513293,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:44:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cca5c008dcf794c1097bc0f4e19dd85c7e08c808","tid":2513293,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:44:51.000Z","msg":"推多下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b5c598aebb90b588265a50ea74b786d74c290c","tid":2513293,"uid":54721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:44:54.000Z","msg":"咁大問題<br />\n唔係比人炒你都唔拎出黎"},{"pid":"dc3b1c9db88932c76bd5f0c2972a0941e9c10409","tid":2513293,"uid":143642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:44:56.000Z","msg":"仆街屌 食腸粉定食老鼠屎。。"},{"pid":"b47da3eb839c68966291d57bfbabb1c89eba8732","tid":2513293,"uid":238803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:45:00.000Z","msg":"啲老鼠屎痾係腸粉皮上面？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e26428a2ee3f281f3a919fd331a9cf144375d52","tid":2513293,"uid":307010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:45:16.000Z","msg":"哇屌"},{"pid":"07e66f28c7e827302219e240a9ba5099c7b28975","tid":2513293,"uid":143642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:46:06.000Z","msg":"唔怪得之前去堂食都聞到一陣陣臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e65483054f208e578c0d78671a426ab14cbfa67","tid":2513293,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:46:12.000Z","msg":"唔好放過呢啲仆街老闆，推起佢"},{"pid":"219a969bfa36d1c3fb6cb23bc90199a4f3d6b8bf","tid":2513293,"uid":337199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:46:44.000Z","msg":"懶人總結<br />\n1.離職7日後老細唔出糧仲要大大聲<br />\n2.去勞工處就同積金局就威脅我,有哂我個人資料要攬炒<br />\n3.極多老鼠同老鼠屎,又污糟<br />\n4.黑心<br />\n5.衛生環境十分惡劣<br />\n6.7成都係大陸,淘寶野"},{"pid":"d308e3b7f07206c5f7533831036fc0aec55430e3","tid":2513293,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:47:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f9263a8dbd3583b928182773049756d47ec379","tid":2513293,"uid":143642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:47:13.000Z","msg":"推呀dnlm"},{"pid":"7d4dbf5f83ed8eea570678544a8e408016172379","tid":2513293,"uid":33694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:47:27.000Z","msg":"痴撚線公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"404b8ef2c0d775ae3d7e27d9683dadcace253cf0","tid":2513293,"uid":143642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:47:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8c700a87a965d0cadb0bbc2106cf22627b58a85d","tid":2513293,"uid":143642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:47:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bbdf7ffb944724b2639b3b6de789efac7b3aa47d","tid":2513293,"uid":251207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:47:53.000Z","msg":"做臭黃店個朵咪呢啲仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔知係咪藍屍扮手足俾屎大家食"},{"pid":"29b7bc0fca41d82de1ed5ed5e5b25e7da5501e3b","tid":2513293,"uid":1394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:49:19.000Z","msg":"好多米奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6b3066ea7437e0c90ca855b04b8fb403162f99","tid":2513293,"uid":143642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:49:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c34e91faddbfe2877959919e4fdbe8c11bc65d3","tid":2513293,"uid":151539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:49:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff2559bfbf8acbe56ea19387b1b545d892ab8461","tid":2513293,"uid":48064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:50:04.000Z","msg":"痴線我仲諗住好耐無食諗住過兩日黎食添<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}